title: S1: audioBoom Q&A Pt.1: Rabia Chaudry
description:
Rabia Chaudry answers listener questions about the case of Adnan Syed. This interview includes questions from Annemarie Amoedo, Earl Adsley, Haley Robinson, Kylie Johnston and Stella Porto.

Produced for audioBoom by Jeremy Helton and Carl Scott. Music by @thesonicdrifter
